{"tid":2417043,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[片]香港要單車踩出馬路,但將所有責任擺哂駕車人士身上真係好離譜","createTime":"2021-02-21T14:02:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T14:22:41.000Z","uid":134683,"like":41,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"036b67d30802152e1b746f3036643087c475991f","tid":2417043,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T14:02:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WKFWs5kRh3I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWKFWs5kRh3I&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDYxAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=8d9b1a66\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WKFWs5kRh3I</a><br />\n<br />\n我諗揸過車既都會遇過啲唔識道路安全既黐線單車手<br />\n好似段片入面咁<br />\n硬cut 3條線、唔睇燈、放綠燈仲係成排車面前慢慢行、逆線...全部都可以致命<br />\n運輸署得一個咁既網頁教單車手道路安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.td.gov.hk/tc/road_safety/safe_cycling_guides/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.td.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Froad_safety%2Fsafe_cycling_guides%2Findex.html&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDYxAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=380e5eec\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.td.gov.hk/tc/road_safety/safe_cycling_guides/index.html</a><br />\n最黐線係呢個<br />\n2：16-2：38<br />\n小巴起步單車先至cut埋去<br />\n小巴佬已經冇同佢嘈使開架車<br />\n個白卡佬仲夠膽喺馬路中心追上去小巴度踢車<br />\n政府唔該喺馬路劃返條單車線<br />\n咪撚害啲駕車人士啦仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55ad59d0c1ec70f850a9a894973b9c6c0bcfdcd8","tid":2417043,"uid":145769,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T14:07:49.000Z","msg":"路權撚踩行人路都顛<br />\n<br />\n你慢行佢喝你添阿"},{"pid":"34f4b0a5d433b7d8670d15b2ccb2146b7c571ac0","tid":2417043,"uid":76020,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T14:29:33.000Z","msg":"路權撚又要人當佢係車行馬路，上到馬路又當返自己係人唔撚駛跟渣車規則。十次有八次見到路權撚都係停綫/讓綫/迴旋處直出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc0bcc6c1f59702062eed7ee1a1a05abc4fdccb9","tid":2417043,"uid":78517,"like":5,"dislike":16,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"